what we've now

00:36:39.290 --> 00:36:43.220
seen in eight randomized control
trials in over 6,000 people.

00:36:43.220 --> 00:36:46.860
CBT for insomnia works.

00:36:46.860 --> 00:36:49.580
And if you want to read more,
there's a fascinating paper

00:36:49.580 --> 00:36:52.310
that you can find.

00:36:52.310 --> 00:36:55.130
